Template: jitsi-videobridge/jvb-hostname
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Hostname
 The jisti-videobridge package needs the DNS hostname of your instance.

Template: jitsi-videobridge/advanced
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Advanced Install
 Do you want to select installation parameters instead of the defaults?
 The default installation should give you a working Jitsi Videobridge 
 instance right away, while the advanced one may help you troubleshoot 
 or keep the install minimal..
